==剧情==
该片讲述[[保定市|保定市]]的三轮车司机“刘好”乐观豁达的生活态度和他的丰富人生。<ref>{{cite news|author=|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/2005-04-05/1409694336.html|title=资料：电影《心急吃不了热豆腐》剧情介绍|newspaper=新浪|date=2005-04-05|accessdate=2015-05-10|archive-date=2019-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191015111224/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/2005-04-05/1409694336.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

